# NOTE
If you are building with master branch, please replace references to "5.5.2.Final-SNAPSHOT" with "master"

# Installing Blacktie into JBoss AS

1. Install a WildFly build
Download 10.1.0.Final from http://wildfly.org/downloads/ and unzip

2. Install the BlackTie subsystem into WildFly
unzip wildfly-blacktie-build-${VERSION}-bin.zip into ${WILDFLY_LOCATION}

3. Install the BlackTie administration services into WildFly
copy blacktie-admin-services-ear-*.ear to dir ${WILDFLY_LOCATION}/standalone/deployments

4. Make changes as defined in:
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jbosstm/narayana/5.5.2.Final-SNAPSHOT/blacktie/scripts/hudson/initializeJBoss.xml

# Configuring BlackTie

Edit the setenv.[sh|bat] file as appropriate

# Quickstarts

These can be obtained from http://github.com/jbosstm/quickstart

A good quickstart to begin with is: https://github.com/jbosstm/quickstart/tree/5.5.2.Final-SNAPSHOT/blacktie/xatmi/fooapp

